title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 349-1.5 - Advertising
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12 §§ 349-1.5 - Advertising

State Regulations

All rules and procedures of the chairman relative to
advertising by a physician as set forth in section
325-1.16
of this Title, are made
applicable to therapists. Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 12
§§
349-1.5

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
